OL,3,CMulti-million pound work to restore
OL,4,Charbour left derelict for decades
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FWork to breath new life into Annan
OL,8,FHarbour is now underway.
OL,10,FThe campaign to regenerate the area
OL,11,Fhas been spearheaded Annan Harbour
OL,12,FAction Group (AHAG), who want to
OL,13,Ftransform the harbour into "an
OL,14,Fimportant economic, cultural and
OL,15,Fenvironmental resource for the town's
OL,16,Fresidents and visitors."
