OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F322A1784139506
OL,3,CMulti-million pound work to restore
OL,4,Charbour left derelict for decades
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FThe #15.6 million pound project has
OL,8,Facquired funding from the UK
OL,9,FGovernment's Levelling Up Fund,
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway Council's
OL,11,FCommunity Led Economic Regeneration
OL,12,FFramework and South of Scotland
OL,13,FEnterprise, with Annan Harbour Action
OL,14,FGroup acting as the council's delivery
OL,15,Fpartner.
OL,17,FCarlisle-based construction firm,
OL,18,FCubby Construction, will lead the
OL,19,Fmulti-million pound project.
